**Save all skill files locally:**

The `PRIVATE-TOKEN` header is required for private projects. For public projects, the project skill files (skills.md, issues.md, epics.md, labels.md) can be fetched without a token — omit the `-H` flag for those if the project is public. The users skill always requires a token.

```bash
